title: [Caffe2] Failing to run "./scripts/build_android.sh -DANDROID_TOOLCHAIN=clang"
body_html:
🐛 Bug

I am trying to get this to run: https://github.com/t-vi/AICamera/ -- currently the only supported implementation of AICamera it appears out there since the other one is old & has many compilation issues.

I am following this blog post: https://lernapparat.de/pytorch-android/

When I run ./scripts/build_android.sh -DANDROID_TOOLCHAIN=clang I get this failure:
https://gist.github.com/Suhail/2802c407a2899bae7ba6e8dba9d5ca76

Any ideas?
